    <Network>bridge</Network>
    <Privileged>false</Privileged>
    <Support>https://github.com/Flixorui/flixor/issues</Support>
    <Project>https://github.com/Flixorui/flixor</Project>
    <Overview>
        A fast, Netflix‑style web app, Android, iOS, and MacOS for your Plex library. Browse beautiful rows, see rich details (IMDb/Rotten Tomatoes), and play instantly in your browser with built‑in DASH/HLS playback. Works on any modern desktop or mobile browser. &#xD;
        &#xD;
        This is the backend component.
    </Overview>
